snippet.title: Mobile Editing 101: Adobe Premiere Rush with Amber Torrealba
snippet.description:
Join the VidCon Now Discord: https://bit.ly/VidConNowDiscord

Creating standout content, quickly, is necessary to keep up with content demand. Editing on mobile can help you stay ahead of your posting schedule by allowing you to work wherever you want, whenever you want. Join Amber Torrealba, social media influencer and Adobe Brand Ambassador, to learn how to go from shoot to publish all on mobile using Adobe Premiere Rush, the first all-in-one, cross-device video editing app. 

***************
Register for VidCon Now: www.vidcon.com

New sessions every week. See agenda: http://vidcon.com/now/agenda
Discord: bit.ly/VidConNowDiscord
Twitter: http://twitter.com/vidcon
Facebook: http://facebook.com/vidcon
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/vidcon/
